  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_allred_score">Allred Score</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person_score">PERSON SCORE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_allred_score">Allred Score</xref>
 is used for 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 with breast cancer during a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_cancer_care_spell">Cancer Care Spell</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
There are two types of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_allred_score">Allred Score</xref>:        </p>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Estrogen Receptor (ER)</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Progesterone Receptor (PR).</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ol>
  </div>
